cription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "In the Name of Allah, the most Gracious, the most Merciful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "(Shuru karta hu) Allah ke naam se Jo bada maher-baan nehaayat rahem karne waala hai.", "Urdu": "اللہ کے نام سے (شروع کرتا ہوں) جو بڑا مہربا ن نہایت رحم کرنے والا ہے۔", "RArabic": "BISMILLAAHIR RAHMAANIR RAHEEM", "ArabicText1": "بِسْمِ اللہِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِیْمِ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1012176, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "He completed His blessings upon me and made Paradise lawful for us, and bestowed His nobility to me, and gave me excellence over the women of the world; I ask Him to give my intercession to my descendants and progeny and those, who are devoted to them after me and protect them after me.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Apni ne’mato’n ko mujh par tamaam kiya, aur karaamat o izzat ko mere liye mutabarrik (ba-barkat) kiya, aur apni Jannat se mujhe nawaaza, mai apne farzandaan aur unki awlaado’n aur un se mohabbat karne waalo’n ke liye Jannat ki talab-gaar hu.", "Urdu": "اپنی نعمتوں کومجھ پر تمام کیا، اورکرامت و عزّت کو میرے لئے متبرک کیا، اوراپنی جنت سے مجھے نوازا میں اپنے فرزندان اور انکی اولادوں اور ان سے محبت کرنے والوں کی لئے جنت کی طلب گار ہوں۔", "RArabic": "QAD ATAMMA A’LAYYA NE’MATAHU, WA ABAAHANEE JANNATAHU, WA HANNAANEE KARAAMATAHU, WA FAZZALANEE A’LAA NESAAA-E KHALQEHI, AS-ALOHU AN YOSHAFFE-A’NEE FEE WULDEE WA ZURRIYYATEE WA MAN WADDAHUM BA’DEE WA HAFEZAHUM BA’DEE.", "ArabicText1": "قَدْ اَتَمَّ عَلَيَّ نِعْمَتَهٗ، وَاَبَاحَنِیْ جَنَّتَہٗ، وَهَنَّانِیْ كَرَامَتَہٗ، وَفَضَّلَنِیْ عَلٰي نِسَاۗءِ خَلْقِہٖ، اَسْئَلُہٗ اَنْ یُّشَفِّعَنِیْ فِیْ وُلْدِیْ 